    <deftitle>Marelli IAW 8P.40 Peugeot 106 - Comparison Markup</deftitle>
    <description>Reverse-engineering XDF for a 64 KiB 27C512 dump from Marelli IAW 8P.40. This definition is intentionally conservative and marks checksum words, known 68HC11 vector addresses, first-pass candidate regions, and table/vector candidates supported by stock-vs-MOD2 comparison. Definitions are raw-byte views unless otherwise noted. Version 0.4 adds code-confirmed banked views for the 0x8A68 region and refined 0x89ED-0x8A08 control/vector views.</description>
    <author>OpenAI Codex</author>
    <baseoffset>0</baseoffset>
    <DEFAULTS datasizeinbits="8" sigdigits="2" outputtype="1" signed="0" lsbfirst="0" float="0" />
    <REGION type="0xFFFFFFFF" startaddress="0x0" size="0x10000" regionflags="0x0" name="Binary File" desc="Full 27C512 image" />
